116
00:09:16,480 --> 00:09:17,630
with a few things.

117
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:20,030
Do you still remember

118
00:09:20,880 --> 00:09:23,670
the phone that my dad gave you?

119
00:09:24,375 --> 00:09:26,600
