156
00:10:55,030 --> 00:10:56,880
He is protected by his father's will.

157
00:10:57,320 --> 00:10:58,670
Zhou Wei won't do anything to him.

158
00:10:59,360 --> 00:11:00,150
But for you,

159
00:11:00,670 --> 00:11:02,360
