160
00:11:02,790 --> 00:11:04,430
The best way out right now is

161
00:11:04,910 --> 00:11:06,120
to take his money

162
00:11:06,525 --> 00:11:08,175
and leave the country
till things die down.

163
00:11:08,320 --> 00:11:09,390
Come back in two years.

164
00:11:13,390 --> 00:11:14,200
Of course.

165
00:11:14,360 --> 00:11:15,120
If you think

166
00:11:15,120 --> 00:11:16,720
